"{\"uid\": \"perthnow.com.au-news-business-retail-click-frenzy-travel-sale-olympics-making-you-want-to-go-to-paris-huge-deals-on-travel-kick-off-tonight-c-15621451\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Get the FREE App  Get the FREE App  Planning to get away from your winter blues?\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 80, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Well, here's your sign and a chance to do it on the cheap!\", \"from\": 82, \"to\": 140, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Click Frenzy Travel is launching Wednesday at 5pm WST and offering can not-miss deals, including discounted flights to Paris.\", \"from\": 142, \"to\": 267, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 148, \"end\": 154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frenzy\", \"score\": 0.9999999682604545, \"rank\": 3.173924688886618e-08, \"text\": \"Frenzy\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frenzy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frenzy\"}, {\"begin\": 261, \"end\": 266, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999831743, \"rank\": 1.7024558760572906e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The sale - which will run until 10pm on August 10 - features the best travel providers and their deals across all the major travel categories including flights, accommodation, destination packages, cruises, experiences, tours, and luggage and accessories.\", \"from\": 269, \"to\": 524, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Notable brands offering top travel deals include Jetstar, Celebrity Cruises, RedBalloon, G Adventures, Expedia, Malaysia Airlines, Qatar Airways, Wendy Wu Tours, Oaks Hotels, Greyhound Australia and Scoopon.\", \"from\": 526, \"to\": 733, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 575, \"end\": 582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jetstar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jetstar\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jetstar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jetstar\"}, {\"begin\": 584, \"end\": 601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celebrity_Cruises\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Celebrity Cruises\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celebrity_Cruises\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celebrity_Cruises\"}, {\"begin\": 603, \"end\": 613, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RedBalloon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RedBalloon\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RedBalloon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RedBalloon\"}, {\"begin\": 615, \"end\": 627, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G_Adventures\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"G Adventures\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G_Adventures\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G_Adventures\"}, {\"begin\": 629, \"end\": 636, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Expedia\", \"score\": 0.9999999906003723, \"rank\": 9.399484692847139e-09, \"text\": \"Expedia\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Expedia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Expedia\"}, {\"begin\": 638, \"end\": 646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\", \"score\": 0.9999999960532477, \"rank\": 3.930187790967391e-09, \"text\": \"Malaysia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malaysia\"}, {\"begin\": 657, \"end\": 670, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar_Airways\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Qatar Airways\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar_Airways\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Qatar_Airways\"}, {\"begin\": 672, \"end\": 680, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Photos\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Wendy Wu\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Photos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Photos\"}, {\"begin\": 701, \"end\": 710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greyhound_Lines\", \"score\": 0.9999999949718585, \"rank\": 3.2679334197882155e-09, \"text\": \"Greyhound\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greyhound_Lines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greyhound_Lines\"}, {\"begin\": 711, \"end\": 720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999818101, \"rank\": 1.776698048780777e-11, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Click Frenzy Head of Marketing Daniel Thompson said Australians are cutting costs across the board but surprisingly \\\"travel is not one of them\\\".\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 879, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Aussies are prioritising taking trips - whether local or international - because they are craving that element of fun and escapism in their lives,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 1038, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are thrilled to be bringing back some amazing travel deals to Australians with another sale this year.\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1146, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We have you covered, from incredible international flight deals to discounts at top-notch local hotels.\\\"\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1251, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"TOP-FLIGHT DEALS:  \\u25cfQatar Airways: 12 per cent off flights to Paris and other European destinations  \\u25cfJetstar: Fly to Japan and Return for FREE  TOP-CRUISE DEALS:  \\u25cfNorwegian Cruise Lines: Save up to $2,500 off Cruises to Europe, Hawaii, Asia and more!\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1505, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1315, \"end\": 1320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999831743, \"rank\": 1.7024558760572906e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1371, \"end\": 1376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.9984130940858196, \"rank\": 0.0015871204614310646, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 1483, \"end\": 1489, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\", \"score\": 0.999999997505256, \"rank\": 2.486869227358227e-09, \"text\": \"Hawaii\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hawaii\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u25cfCelebrity Cruises: Save up to 75 per cent Off Second Guest, and additional savings of up to $300 per room  \\u25cf Quark Expeditions 40 per cent off select Arctic and Antarctic voyages to Canadian Arctic to Greenland to Svalbard  TOP EXPERIENCES & PACKAGE DEALS:  \\u25cfG Adventures: 25 per cent off select tours in South Africa, Argentina and Cambodia  \\u25cf G Adventures: 15 per cent off select tours in Vietnam, Maldives, Costa Rica, Mexico + MORE  \\u25cf RedBalloon: Take an extra 5 per cent off sitewide  \\u25cf Halong Tours: 65 per cent off tour of Vietnam  \\u25cf Scoopon: $399 all-inclusive Bali packages for 7 nights with 2 adults  \\u25cf Scoopon: $499 all-inclusive Thailand packages for 5 nights with 2 adults  \\u25cf Klook: 30 per cent off tours to Bali  \\u25cf Klook: 20 per cent off USA tours, including the Hollywood Sign, Kualoa Ranch and more  \\u25cf Klook: 20 per cent off tours to Japan, including bar crawls, Mount Fuji and street go-karting  TOP ACCOMMODATION DEALS:  \\u25cf Oaks Hotels: 30 per cent off 2-night stay across 55 Australian & NZ locations  \\u25cf AUS Weekend Escape: 30 per cent off 20 hotels nationwide  \\u25cfScoopon: Australia deals from $269 for 2 nights for 2 adults save up to 69 per cent  \\u25cf Klook: Up to 20 per cent off Japan and Bali Hotels and Resorts  \\u25cf GrabOne: Up to 60 per cent Off Hotels, NZ stay at Cordis Hotel, Hammer Spring Hotels, Mercure Hotel and more!\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 2851, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1709, \"end\": 1718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greenland\", \"score\": 0.9999998242342526, \"rank\": 1.6161325359175442e-07, \"text\": \"Greenland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greenland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greenland\"}, {\"begin\": 1722, \"end\": 1730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Svalbard\", \"score\": 0.9999999997226041, \"rank\": 2.221553385191606e-10, \"text\": \"Svalbard\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Svalbard\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Svalbard\"}, {\"begin\": 1813, \"end\": 1825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999769033823, \"rank\": 1.687108738475205e-08, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 1827, \"end\": 1836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina\", \"score\": 0.9998908945524532, \"rank\": 0.00010693129176599367, \"text\": \"Argentina\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argentina\"}, {\"begin\": 1841, \"end\": 1849, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cambodia\", \"score\": 0.9999999999126885, \"rank\": 7.292139428886984e-11, \"text\": \"Cambodia\", \"types\